title: 10/15/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 10/15/21 DPS Best Of
description:
Former NFL QB Brady Quinn joins Dan Patrick on The Dan Patrick Show. Brady shares a Jon Gruden story and spends some time previewing this week's College Football action. MLB Network's Harold Reynold recaps last night Giants/Dodgers game and discusses whether or not there should be replay for check swings. Plus, host of the Ross Tucker Football Podcast & CBS/Westwood One color analyst Ross Tucker joins Dan Patrick. Ross was at the Eagles/Buccaneers game and recaps all the action.
